</div><div id="newscolumn"><h3><span>Sakura-Con, Ships Ahoy, San Japan and&hellip; sssDiscord</span></h3>
<h4 class="date">March 19, 2018</h4>
<div id="newscontent"><p>When we started rolling out our <strong><a href="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/roundup/">Weekly Roundup email,</a></strong> a three-panel comic shipping various romantic pairings seemed like an obvious fit. But did you know they began as an idea for our supporter/membership thing, <a href="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/store/bci.html">Bittersweet Club International?</a></p>
<p class="img"><img src="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/misc/news/march18_dxl@2x.png" width="520" height="245" alt="David loves Lucy"></p>
<p>Well, today they find their way home. <strong>The latest addition to the mountain of member-exclusive comics is the first &ldquo;season&rdquo; of Ships Ahoy,</strong> the nineteen strips that started it all!! We think it&rsquo;s a nice treat for any members who missed them in the early emails.</p>
<p class="button"><a href="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/store/bci.html">Join Bittersweet Club International!</a></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/store/bci.html">$45 a year</a></strong> gets you a keychain, embossed card, surprise gifts and access to 400+ pages of bonus comics! Like, say, the one where Augustus and Lucy meet as kids&hellip;</p>
<p class="img"><a href="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/store/bci.html"><img src="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/misc/news/playdate_clipping@2x.png" width="344" height="400" alt="A clipping from the Play Date comic."></a></p>
<p>The other big mid-March news is&hellip; <strong>we&rsquo;re soon heading to Seattle for <a href="http://sakuracon.org">Sakura-Con!!</a></strong> It begins Friday, March 30 and continues over Easter weekend!</p>
<p class="img"><a href="http://sakuracon.org"><img src="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/misc/news/newyear2018_sakuracon@2x.jpg" width="520" height="124" alt="Sakura-Con 2018"></a></p>
<p>Come bring us your best authentic Starbucks coffees and Amazon shipping boxes. We love Sakura-Con! It&rsquo;s been a while! Come back and say hello!!</p>
<p>And if you can&rsquo;t?? Well, <strong><a href="http://www.anime-expo.org">see us in LA this July 5,</a></strong> or, for the first time, <strong>BCB IS SAYING &ldquo;HOWDY&rdquo; TO TEXAS!!</strong> That&rsquo;s <strong><a href="https://san-japan.org">San Japan</a></strong> in <strong>San Antonio, August 31&ndash;September 2!!</strong> All customers must wear ten-gallon hats and call us varmints.</p>
<p class="img"><a href="https://bcb.cat/discord"><img src="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/misc/news/march18_discord@2x.jpg" width="520" height="333" alt="The BCB Discord server"></a></p>
<p><strong><a href="http://bcb.cat/discord">You&rsquo;re invited to our Discord server!</a></strong> It has so much now! Everyone&rsquo;s entering <a href="https://www.bittersweetcandybowl.com/candybooru/post/view/13340">the art contest!!</a> Cool kids are <a href="https://www.patreon.com/settings/account">linking their Patreon accounts and getting gold names!</a> Everybody picks &ldquo;Team <em>_</em>_&rdquo; roles for the characters they support! There&rsquo;s a bot that tells you your fortune or punches you in the face or something! It&rsquo;s all here and it&rsquo;s all wonderful!</p>
<p class="button"><a href="https://bcb.cat/discord">Join the BCB Discord server!</a></p>

<p class="signoff">&mdash; Oliver</p>
</div>
